data.description: Stunning townhome located in the highly desirable community of Perkasie Woods. This unit features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, finished basement with walkout to rear yard, maintenance free composite deck and 1 car garage. Wide open floor plan features hardwood floors throughout the living room, dining room and kitchen with island, recessed lighting, granite countertops, backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. Just outside from the kitchen is a large maintenance free deck perfect for outdoor entertaining. Upstairs, you will find a spacious primary suite with a large walk-in closet and private bathroom. Private bathroom features a double sink vanity and ceramic tile in the shower and floor. Two additional generous sized bedrooms, hall bath with ceramic tile and laundry room complete the second floor. Walkout lower level recreation room features a finished living area with recessed lighting, access to the garage and sliding doors to the rear yard.  This space is large enough for entertaining, home office, playroom, exercise room, or whatever fits your needs. Community playground with walking trails and Lenape Park is a short walk away. Make your appointment today!
